				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Reasonable expected twist?<a name="27776"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 15 04 12:00 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Both Chant of Battle &amp; Guardian Rhythms give AC.  
<br />

<br />
Chant gives STR + AC
<br />
Rhythms gives MR + AC
<br />

<br />
So, figure what you need most.  If you're fighting something that casts, maybe Rhythms is more helpful.  Otherwise, maybe Chant is more helpful--more STR means your melees hit harder more often.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
