				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Reasonable expected twist?<a name="27907"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 15 04 7:37 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The thing with twisting more than three is you bump into the zero-duration song bug:
<br />

<br />
You slow down.
<br />
Your feet move faster.
<br />
You slow down.
<br />

<br />
... all in the course of a split second.
<br />

<br />
The really evil thing about that bug is that it is client specific.  That means that even though you have four songs up in your song window, your party may not.  For that reason, I stick to three songs unless there is a compelling reason to do otherwise.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
