				<td colspan="2"><span>I normally twist 2 or 3 songs only. I am a little older so I pace myself to minimize wrist and hand pain.  My question is:  when I am fighting, normally one of my songs is a slow / snare and the other songs are group buffs.  So a group may only see one or two songs playing when really I have 2 or 3 on.  Do most of you just twist 3 group buffs?  Ideally, it would be nice to have both a slower and snarer in a group, but that doesn't happen all the time.  So I find that many times I need to be the slower or snarer.</span></td>
